MyBroadband has launched its 2018 South Africa IT salary survey, which will provide insight into the salaries of ICT professionals in the country – Complete the survey here. MyBroadband’s annual IT salary survey is completed by thousands of IT professionals, managers, and executives, and provides an accurate view of real-world salaries. It is completely anonymous, no identifying information is recorded, and only takes a minute to complete. You can also win R3,000 cash, an Amazon Fire TV, and branded gear by completing the survey. Your feedback is very important to ensure we give an accurate reflection of IT salaries in South Africa.